snippet.title: Warhammer 40.000 Gladius - Tyranids || Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Gladius' Tyranids DLC is OUT NOW!
🎮 Get it on Steam 👉 http://bit.ly/2T3cKpK
💬 Join the Discord Server 👉 https://discord.gg/CyBavXBcad
🦎 Get it on Slitherine Store 👉 https://bit.ly/35dpqTM

On Gladius Prime there is only war. Orks, Necrons, and Men vie for control of a dying world. But something worse lurks in the shadows. Feral Tyranids now roam the surface of the planet, escapees from an Imperial research facility. All life on Gladius will shudder in fear. For the Great Devourer comes.
